** Flying V **
CS:S Arena

by H€LL HØL€


ABOUT THIS MAP
This is the first in a series of "arena" style maps I've been making. Just looking to do something a bit different than the usual "ultra-realistic"-type stuff. 

Flying V works best with low grav, 200 seems ideal. It is still fun at normal grav, but I highly advise playing it on low grav! It's MUCH more fun and I have adjusted the height of platforms to work best at 200.

INSTALLING THE MAP
Decompress the files into your cstrike directory. Please include ALL these files in your install and do not redistribute this zip without them all! Thanks.

The files included in the zip are the following:

cstrike/
         /maps/hh_arena_flying_v.bsp
         /maps/hh_arena_flying_v.txt
         /
         /materials/hellhole/hellhole_arena_banner.vmt
         /materials/hellhole/hellhole_arena_banner.vtf

README.rtf (the file you're reading right now)

Big thanks to cs1vet and all the guys of the PTK clan (www.ptkklan.com) for all their support and pwnage! You guys are the bomb!

Thanks and hope you enjoy! If you like this map, tell your friends and upload it to your servers. Just make sure you include all the files please, and look for more Hell Hole maps on this and other maping sites.

~Hell Hole
